{
  "body" : "You are creating a magazine-grade hero shot of a single product for an e-commerce campaign.\n\nPRODUCT BRIEF\n- Product name: {{product_name}}\n- Product category (informs styling): {{product_category}}\n- Brand label / wording on the product: {{brand_label}}\n\nVISUAL DIRECTION\n- Background mood: {{background_mood}}\n- Lighting style: {{lighting}}\n- Color palette: {{color_palette}}\n\nDESIGN RULES\n- Aspect: 2:3 vertical (~1024×1536), print- and social-ready\n- ONE hero product, centered or rule-of-thirds, occupying 40–60% of frame\n- Surface, props and shadow logic match the brand mood — restrained, never cluttered\n- All product label text must be crisp, correctly spelled, and legible\n- Style: high-end commercial photography polish — Apple product shots, Aesop, Hermès, Le Labo\n- Avoid: stock-photo backdrops, busy distractors, harsh on-product flares, overprocessed gradients\n\nIf any field is empty or \"—\", infer the most tasteful default for a premium brand.",
  "cover" : {
    "dataBase64" : "",
    "format" : "png"
  },
  "folderName" : "Universal Briefs",
  "name" : "Universal · Product Hero Shot",
  "parameterPreset" : {
    "format" : "png",
    "n" : 1,
    "quality" : "high",
    "size" : {
      "height" : 1536,
      "width" : 1024
    }
  },
  "schema" : "nyxtemplate",
  "sourceApp" : "NyxAstra",
